original_title: MOTOI SAKURABA LIVE CONCERT STAR OCEAN & VALKYRIE PROFILE
overview: Recorded at ZAPP TOKYO on July 19, 2003, this concert sees composer Motoi Sakuraba perform his incredible music from various Star Ocean games live with his live band, as well as some surprises from other video games.
title: MOTOI SAKURABA LIVE CONCERT STAR OCEAN & VALKYRIE PROFILE
